se\":\"p\",\"trial_type\":\"html-keyboard-response\",\"trial_index\":412,\"time_elapsed\":1827329,\"internal_node_id\":\"0.0-369.0\",\"final_zoom_factor\":0.5478961504028648,\"blue_key\":\"P\",\"green_key\":\"Q\",\"correctCount\":11,\"total_n_questions\":12,\"quiz_passed\":true,\"practice\":false,\"choice\":\"blue\",\"trial\":4,\"city\":32,\"grid_id\":1,\"cityID\":16,\"path_chosen\":\"blue\",\"button_pressed\":\"p\",\"reaction_time_ms\":3616,\"key_assignment\":{\"blue\":\"P\",\"green\":\"Q\"},\"path_A_expected_cost\":-3.157814142425087,\"path_B_expected_cost\":-4.919015167300093,\"path_A_actual_cost\":-4,\"path_B_actual_cost\":-7,\"path_A_future_overlap\":0,\"path_B_future_overlap\":0,\"dominant_axis_A\":\"horizontal\",\"dominant_axis_B\":\"vertical\",\"abstract_sequence_A\":[[1,7]],\"abstract_sequence_B\":[[7,1]],\"better_path\":\"a\",\"chose_better_path\":1,\"participant\":201,\"context\":\"row\",\"objective\":\"costs\",\"grid\":1,\"start_A\":[2,0],\"start_B\":[7,4],\"goal_A\":[1,7],\"goal_B\":[0,3],\"path_A\":[[2,0],[2,1],[2,2],[2,3],[2,4],[2,5],[2,6],[2,7],[1,7]],\"path_B\":[[7,4],[7,3],[6,3],[5,3],[4,3],[3,3],[2,3],[1,3],[0,3]],\"path_A_actions\":[1,1,1,1,1,1,1,2],\"path_B_actions\":[3,2,2,2,2,2,2,2],\"path_A_future_row_overlap\":0,\"path_B_future_row_overlap\":0,\"path_A_future_col_overlap\":0,\"path_B_future_col_overlap\":0,\"path_A_future_row_and_col_overlap\":0,\"path_B_future_row_and_col_overlap\":0,\"path_A_future_rel_overlap\":0,\"path_B_future_rel_overlap\":0,\"path_A_future_irrel_overlap\":0,\"path_B_future_irrel_overlap\":0,\"bonus_accuracy\":0.75},{\"trial_type\":\"html-keyboard-response\",\"trial_index\":413,\"time_elapsed\":1832213,\"internal_node_id\":\"0.0-370.0\",\"final_zoom_factor\":0.5478961504028648,\"blue_key\":\"P\",\"green_key\":\"Q\",\"correctCount\":11,\"total_n_questions\":12,\"quiz_passed\":true,\"bonus_accuracy\":0.75},{\"rt\":3632,\"response\":\" \",\"trial_type\":\"html-keyboard-response\",\"trial_index\":414,\"time_elapsed\":1835847,\"internal_node_id\":\"0.0-371.0\",\"final_zoom_factor\":0.5478961504028648,\"blue_key\":\"P\",\"green_key\":\"Q\",\"correctCount\":11,\"total_n_questions\":12,\"quiz_passed\":true,\"bonus_accuracy\":0.75},{\"rt\":154671,\"response\":{\"strategy\":\"I picked P or Q on the first route based on the future routes for each day - one option usually gave me one box more of information (e.g. whether it was grey or red/green) that was useful for future routes (in pink), which I could use to plan which future routes to take as it would give me an idea of whether it was a tip/toll column/row or not.\"},\"trial_type\":\"survey-text\",\"trial_index\":415,\"time_elapsed\":1990570,\"internal_node_id\":\"0.0-372.0\",\"final_zoom_factor\":0.5478961504028648,\"blue_key\":\"P\",\"green_key\":\"Q\",\"correctCount\":11,\"total_n_questions\":12,\"quiz_passed\":true,\"bonus_accuracy\":0.75},{\"rt\":78818,\"response\":{\"tips_vs_tolls\":\"If it was a tip day then I tried to avoid grey boxes, whereas on toll days I of course tried to only hit grey boxes! However, my strategy to discover which rows/columns were which colour did not differ on the different types of days.\"},\"trial_type\":\"survey-text\",\"trial_index\":416,\"time_elapsed\":2069391,\"internal_node_id\":\"0.0-373.0\",\"final_zoom_factor\":0.5478961504028648,\"blue_key\":\"P\",\"green_key\":\"Q\",\"correctCount\":11,\"total_n_questions\":12,\"quiz_passed\":true,\"bonus_accuracy\":0.75},{\"rt\":130636,\"response\":{\"rows_vs_columns\":\"On column days I was more careful about picking routes that mostly followed columns (as it could mean hitting lots of one colour in one go, which could be good or bad), whereas rows were 'easier' options if I wasn't sure (as I was at least much less likely to hit all reds etc.) I used this strategy but opposite on row days.\"},\"trial_type\":\"survey-text\",\"trial_index\":417,\"time_elapsed\":2200029,\"internal_node_id\":\"0.0-374.0\",\"final_zoom_factor\":0.5478961504028648,\"blue_key\":\"P\",\"green_key\":\"Q\",\"correctCount\":11,\"total_n_questions\":12,\"quiz_passed\":true,\"bonus_accuracy\":0.75},{\"rt\":122308,\"response\":{\"lookahead\":\"I didn't really look at upcoming jobs individually - I generally looked to see how many pink squares I could guess the colour of by finding out the colour of another square when choosing my routes rather than seeing if I could secure one 'perfect' route later. Basically, I looked ahead at future jobs as a whole rather than individual future jobs.\"},\"trial_type\":\"survey-text\",\"trial_index\":418,\"time_elapsed\":2322339,\"internal_node_id\":\"0.0-375.0\",\"final_zoom_factor\":0.5478961504028648,\"blue_key\":\"P\",\"green_key\":\"Q\",\"correctCount\":11,\"total_n_questions\":12,\"quiz_passed\":true,\"bonus_accuracy\":0.75},{\"rt\":139604,\"response\":{\"other_comments\":\"I think the experiment as a whole has been easy to understand and work with (the taxi part was quite fun!) but the text boxes at the end (like the one I am currently writing in) are quite small compared to the rest of the screen - so if this experiment is run again that is something to fix!\"},\"trial_type\":\"survey-text\",\"trial_index\":419,\"time_elapsed\":2461945,\"internal_node_id\":\"0.0-376.0\",\"final_zoom_factor\":0.5478961504028648,\"blue_key\":\"P\",\"green_key\":\"Q\",\"correctCount\":11,\"total_n_questions\":12,\"quiz_passed\":true,\"bonus_accuracy\":0.75},{\"rt\":4968,\"response\":\" \",\"trial_type\":\"html-keyboard-response\",\"trial_index\":420,\"time_elapsed\":2466914,\"internal_node_id\":\"0.0-377.0\",\"final_zoom_factor\":0.5478961504028648,\"blue_key\":\"P\",\"green_key\":\"Q\",\"correctCount\":11,\"total_n_questions\":12,\"quiz_passed\":true,\"bonus_accuracy\":0.75},{\"rt\":28377,\"response\":{\"NFC1.\":\"somewhat characteristic of me\",\"NFC2.\":\"somewhat characteristic of me\",\"NFC3.\":\"extremely uncharacteristic of me\",\"NFC4.\":\"extremely uncharacteristic of me\",\"NFC5.\":\"extremely uncharacteristic of me\